# CodeBook

Description Variables: 

Subject:  Subject ID
Activity: Type of activity performed when measurements were taken (See 'Activities')

# Features

'-XYZ' is used to denote 3-axial signals in the X, Y and Z directions.

- Mean time for acceleration of body
 
TimeBodyAccelerometerMean()-X                
TimeBodyAccelerometerMean()-Y             
TimeBodyAccelerometerMean()-Z

- Mean time of acceleration of gravity

TimeGravityAccelerometerMean()-X             
TimeGravityAccelerometerMean()-Y             
TimeGravityAccelerometerMean()-Z 

- Mean time of body acceleration jerk

TimeBodyAccelerometerJerkMean()-X            
TimeBodyAccelerometerJerkMean()-Y            
TimeBodyAccelerometerJerkMean()-Z 

- Mean body gyroscope measurement

TimeBodyGyroscopeMean()-X                    
TimeBodyGyroscopeMean()-Y                    
TimeBodyGyroscopeMean()-Z  

- Mean jerk signal of body gyroscope

TimeBodyGyroscopeJerkMean()-X                
TimeBodyGyroscopeJerkMean()-Y                
TimeBodyGyroscopeJerkMean()-Z

- Mean magnitude of body/gravity (jerk) Accelerotion

TimeBodyAccelerometerMagnitudeMean()         
TimeGravityAccelerometerMagnitudeMean()      
TimeBodyAccelerometerJerkMagnitudeMean()     

- Mean magnitude of body gyroscope (jerk) measurement

TimeBodyGyroscopeMagnitudeMean()             
TimeBodyGyroscopeJerkMagnitudeMean()    

- Mean frequency of body acceleration

FrequencyBodyAccelerometerMean()-X           
FrequencyBodyAccelerometerMean()-Y           
FrequencyBodyAccelerometerMean()-Z

- Mean frequency of body accerlation jerk

FrequencyBodyAccelerometerJerkMean()-X       
FrequencyBodyAccelerometerJerkMean()-Y       
FrequencyBodyAccelerometerJerkMean()-Z

- Mean frequency of body gyroscope measurement

FrequencyBodyGyroscopeMean()-X              
FrequencyBodyGyroscopeMean()-Y               
FrequencyBodyGyroscopeMean()-Z


- Mean frequency of body acceleration (jerk) magnitude

FrequencyBodyAccelerometerMagnitudeMean()   
FrequencyBodyAccelerometerJerkMagnitudeMean()

- Mean frequency of magnitude of body gyroscope (jerk) measurement

FrequencyBodyGyroscopeMagnitudeMean()        
FrequencyBodyGyroscopeJerkMagnitudeMean() 

- Standard deviation of time for acceleration of body

TimeBodyAccelerometerSTD()-X                 
TimeBodyAccelerometerSTD()-Y                 
TimeBodyAccelerometerSTD()-Z  

- Standard deviation of time of acceleration of gravity

TimeGravityAccelerometerSTD()-X              
TimeGravityAccelerometerSTD()-Y              
TimeGravityAccelerometerSTD()-Z     

- Standard deviation of time of body acceleration jerk

TimeBodyAccelerometerJerkSTD()-X             
TimeBodyAccelerometerJerkSTD()-Y             
TimeBodyAccelerometerJerkSTD()-Z  

- Standard deviation of body gyroscope measurement

TimeBodyGyroscopeSTD()-X                    
TimeBodyGyroscopeSTD()-Y                     
TimeBodyGyroscopeSTD()-Z  

- Standard deviation of jerk signal of body

TimeBodyGyroscopeJerkSTD()-X                 
TimeBodyGyroscopeJerkSTD()-Y                 
TimeBodyGyroscopeJerkSTD()-Z   

- Standard deviation of magnitude of body/gravity (jerk) Acceloration

TimeBodyAccelerometerMagnitudeSTD()          
TimeGravityAccelerometerMagnitudeSTD()       
TimeBodyAccelerometerJerkMagnitudeSTD()

- Standard deviation of magnitude of body gyroscope (jerk) measurement

TimeBodyGyroscopeMagnitudeSTD()              
TimeBodyGyroscopeJerkMagnitudeSTD()

- Standard deviation of frequency of body acceleration

FrequencyBodyAccelerometerSTD()-X            
FrequencyBodyAccelerometerSTD()-Y            
FrequencyBodyAccelerometerSTD()-Z  

- Standard deviation frequency of body accerlation jerk

FrequencyBodyAccelerometerJerkSTD()-X        
FrequencyBodyAccelerometerJerkSTD()-Y        
FrequencyBodyAccelerometerJerkSTD()-Z 

- Standard deviation frequency of body gyroscope measurement

FrequencyBodyGyroscopeSTD()-X                
FrequencyBodyGyroscopeSTD()-Y                
FrequencyBodyGyroscopeSTD()-Z      

- Standard deviation of frequency of body acceleration (jerk) magnitude

FrequencyBodyAccelerometerMagnitudeSTD()     
FrequencyBodyAccelerometerJerkMagnitudeSTD() 

- Standard deviation frequency of magnitude of body gyroscope (jerk) measurement

FrequencyBodyGyroscopeMagnitudeSTD()    
FrequencyBodyGyroscopeJerkMagnitudeSTD()

